msgctxt "talk00"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Oh dear, oh dear...<2.pa> <3.se_co>Lightning<4.re_co> strikes this\n"
"stable so often, I get nervous whenever\n"
"it rains even a little.\n"
"I just don't understand why it strikes so\n"
"often...<5.pa> <6.so>Hey, it's a long shot, but if you\n"
"have some time, could you find out why?<7.ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
#. 3: set_colour (red)
#. 4: reset_colour
#. 5: pause (short)
#. 6: choice
msgctxt "talk01"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Have you...<2.pa>have you decided to\n"
"help me? Please figure out why <3.se_co>lightning<4.re_co>\n"
"keeps hitting this stable!<5.pa> Please!<6.ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
#. 3: pause (short)
#. 4: set_colour (red)
#. 5: reset_colour
msgctxt "talk02"
msgid ""
"<1.so>*sigh*<2.pa> I get scared in the evening...<3.pa> \n"
"I wonder why the <4.se_co>lightning <5.re_co>seems to\n"
"have it out for this place."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "talk04"
msgid "<1.so>I can finally relax!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "talk05"
msgid "<1.so>Urrrm...run away..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
#. 3: set_colour (red)
#. 4: reset_colour
#. 5: choice
msgctxt "talk06"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Please... Help!<2.pa> Stop the<3.se_co> lightning<4.re_co>!\n"
"Please find out why it keeps striking\n"
"this stable!<5.ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (15f)
#. 3: pause (15f)
msgctxt "talk07"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Aiiiiieeee! I just...can't...<2.pa>\n"
"I'm so scared...<3.pa>\n"
"Please find out why this is happening!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
#. 3: pause (15f)
#. 4: set_colour (red)
#. 5: reset_colour
#. 6: pause (15f)
#. 7: choice
msgctxt "talk08"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Eeeeyah! I've had it...<2.pa> I can't handle this\n"
"constant fear.<3.pa>\n"
"\n"
"<4.se_co>Lightning<5.re_co> strikes this stable really often, \n"
"so I get scared whenever it starts to\n"
"rain...<6.pa>\n"
"Please... Could you go try and find out\n"
"why this keeps happening?<7.ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "talk09"
msgid ""
"<1.so>You will?! Really? I'm so happy!\n"
"I'm counting on you."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
#. 3: pause (short)
msgctxt "talk10"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I see...<2.pa> Well, I guess it can't be helped.<3.pa>\n"
"*sigh*"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
#. 3: set_colour (red)
#. 4: reset_colour
